sequenceDiagram
    participant WV as WebView<br/>(React)
    participant MB as MessageBroker
    participant FS as FlowService
    participant ES as ExecutionService
    participant DS as DebugService

    Note over WV, DS: フロー読み込み
    WV->>MB: flow:load
    MB->>FS: loadFlow(id)
    FS-->>MB: FlowDefinition
    MB-->>WV: flow:loaded

    Note over WV, DS: フロー保存
    WV->>MB: flow:save
    MB->>FS: saveFlow(data)
    FS-->>MB: 保存結果
    MB-->>WV: flow:saved

    Note over WV, DS: フロー実行
    WV->>MB: flow:execute
    MB->>ES: executeFlow(id)
    loop ノードごと
        ES-->>MB: execution:nodeStarted
        MB-->>WV: execution:nodeStarted
        ES-->>MB: execution:nodeCompleted
        MB-->>WV: execution:nodeCompleted
    end
    ES-->>MB: execution:flowCompleted
    MB-->>WV: execution:flowCompleted

    Note over WV, DS: デバッグ（ステップ実行）
    WV->>MB: debug:start
    MB->>DS: startDebug(id)
    DS-->>MB: debug:paused
    MB-->>WV: debug:paused
    WV->>MB: debug:step
    MB->>DS: stepNext()
    DS->>ES: executeNode(nodeId)
    ES-->>DS: NodeResult
    DS-->>MB: debug:paused
    MB-->>WV: debug:paused
